<text top="224" left="57" width="124" height="11" font="2"><b>Human Rights Council  </b></text>
<text top="237" left="57" width="81" height="9" font="3"><b>Thirteenth session </b></text>
<text top="249" left="57" width="61" height="9" font="0">Agenda item 3 </text>
<text top="261" left="57" width="225" height="9" font="3"><b>Promotion and protection of all human rights, civil,  </b></text>
<text top="273" left="57" width="198" height="9" font="3"><b>political, economic, social and cultural rights,  </b></text>
<text top="285" left="57" width="150" height="9" font="3"><b>including the right to development </b></text>
